data.description: **Back on market due to buyer non-performance.** Welcome to the highly desirable Avalon Park community! This 3 bed, 2.5 bath former MODEL home is like-new and is situated on an OVERSIZED corner lot! Pride of ownership is seen the moment you arrive at the home. You are immediately greeted by mature landscaping and the fabulous shingle siding above the garage and second floor.  Enter the front door and be in awe of the contemporary design, tons of natural light, and OPEN FLOOR PLAN. The dining room, which showcases a feature wall with decorative molding, opens to the living room and continues into the kitchen. The kitchen is a DREAM with tall wood cabinets, modern granite countertops, stylish backsplash, stainless steel appliances, large island with additional guest seating, and pantry. The split floor plan allows for added privacy as the PRIMARY suite is located on the FIRST FLOOR away from the other 2 bedrooms, which are located upstairs. The primary suite is your own peace of paradise encased in designer decorative walls, with fabulous ENSUITE bathroom featuring dual sink vanities, large tile shower, separate water closet, and MASSIVE WALK IN CLOSET! The half bath is located on the 1st floor for guest use.  Head up the stairs to the 2nd and 3rd spacious bedrooms, that share a full bath. Enjoy a morning cup of coffee or a good book from your patio overlooking the peaceful greenery of the yard. Avalon Park has small town charm where you can enjoy AMENITIES such as 2 community swimming pools, playground, dog park, splash pad, basketball court, neighborhood parks, trails and walkways, and clubhouse! Downtown Avalon Park is under construction and is set to include a 2 acre Community Park with Amphitheater! Conveniently located just minutes away from restaurants, Shops at Wiregrass and other retail shops, SR-54 and I-75! X FLOOD ZONE!
